Detailed Description

Author:
Hans Joachim Ferreau, Andreas Potschka, Christian Kirches
Version:
3.0beta
Date:
2009-2012

Various matrix classes: Abstract base matrix class, dense and sparse matrices, including symmetry exploiting specializations.
